    • compositeView

      @SafeVarargs @Nonnull public static <T> @Nonnull List<T> compositeView(@Nonnull @Nonnull List<T> @Nonnull ... lists)
      Returns a composite view of multiple lists as a single list. The returned list provides a unified view of all elements from the provided lists, in the order they are specified. Changes to the underlying lists will be reflected in the composite view.

      The returned list is un-variable-size, serializable and implements RandomAccess, and is mutable if the corresponding underlying list is mutable.

      Type Parameters:
      T - the component type
      Parameters:
      lists - the lists to be composited as a view
      Returns:
      a composite view of multiple lists
